MAY 2024


Pairings in this report are NOT FINALIZED.

THESE ARE PRELIMINARY (pairings are still in production to increase efficiencies)

- To find a specific BASE select the “find” feature or (Ctrl+F) for “find”, type in the base name
(Re: TORONTO) hit Enter, this will take you to the beginning page of where the pairings for that
base start.
- To find a specific destination simply go to the “find” feature at the top of the document and type
in the city code (Re: LAX, BGI), hit Enter. This will take you to the first pairing containing that
destination. Continue to hit enter to search remaining pairings containing the specified city.
